Virus-infected among populatioon = 0.15

Not virus-infected among population = 0.85

P(+/virus-infects) = 0.98 

P(-/virus-infects) = 0.02

P(+/\negation~virus-infects) = 0.10, 

P(-/~virus-infects) = 0.90

a) 
P(+) = (0.98 + 0.10) / (0.98 + 0.10 + 0.02 + 0.90)

= 1.08 / 2

= 0.59

b) 
= (0.98 * 0.15) / 0.59

= 0.249

c) 
= [0.90 * 0.85] / (1 - 0.59)

= (0.90 * 0.85) / 0.41

= 1.865
